      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must address the specific geometry, flow regime, and operating conditions of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA benchmark centrifugal blood pump geometry under the identical operating conditions specified in the COU. Flow regimes, rotational speeds, and fluid properties match the intended use scenario."
    },
    {
