    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within acceptable uncertainty bounds relative to experimental measurements. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 guidance. The model is accepted for the stated context of use.",
